  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Hand over the country to the Speaker\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The independent parties have issued a statement saying that they are asking the Prime Minister to resign immediately and hand over the country to the speaker to form an all-party government.",
        "The union also states that we appeal to the entire nation to join hands not to turn Sri Lanka into the Libya of South Asia as the economic crisis could open the door for foreign forces to enter the country by turning the economic crisis into a human disaster.",
        "The announcement issued by the Union of Independent Parties last night (13) also states:"
      ],
